PDAX request/response mapping (paths are the documented v1 shapes; `PDAX_BASE_URL` already includes `/api/exchange/v1`):
- `getQuote` → `GET /rates/XLMPHP`; response `{ traded_currency, settlement_currency, price }`; `rate = dec(price)`, `xlmAmount = phpToXlm(phpAmount, rate)`, `expiresAt = now + 90s`.
- `sellCryptoForPhp` → `POST /trades` body `{ traded_currency:"XLM", settlement_currency:"PHP", side:"sell", traded_amount, client_ref }`; response `{ reference }` → `{ tradeRef: reference }`.
- `getTradeStatus` → `GET /trades/{ref}`; response `{ status, settlement_fee, filled_settlement_amount }`; `status` mapped FILLED/SETTLED→`FILLED`, FAILED/CANCELLED→`FAILED`, else `PENDING`.
- `cashOutPhpToBank` → `POST /cash_out` body `{ currency:"PHP", amount, bank_code, account_name, account_number, client_ref }` (no OTP); response `{ reference }` → `{ payoutRef: reference }`.
- `getPayoutStatus` → `GET /cash_out/{ref}`; response `{ status, net_amount }`; mapped SETTLED/COMPLETED→`SETTLED`, FAILED/CANCELLED→`FAILED`, else `PENDING`.
- `withdrawCryptoForRefund` → `POST /crypto_withdrawals` with header `Access-Otp: <generateTotp(totpSecret)>`; response `{ reference }`.

